    <Content>
      The system shall update actuator commands at a fixed control loop frequency of at least 20 Hz to ensure responsive motion control and collision avoidance.
    </Content>
  </Requirement>

  <Requirement ID="LL-INTERF-6.2.3">
    <Type>FR</Type>
